OL,5,G2135 DJ Carey - The Dodger
OL,6,     FDJ goes from the remarkable
OL,7,     F'little fella' on the pitch to a
OL,8,     F'hurling God' winning five
OL,9,     FAll-Irelands and nine All-star
OL,10,     Fmedals. Despite this, strange
OL,11,     Frumours start to swirl.
OL,12,G2235 DJ Carey - The Dodger
OL,13,     FAt the pinnacle of his fame DJ's
OL,14,     Fmarriage ends and the media pursue
OL,15,     Fhim relentlessly. Soon, questions
OL,16,     Fabout his health and finances
OL,17,     Fbecome unavoidable.
OL,18,G2340 Unforgotten
OL,19,     FVarious suspects start to come out
OL,20,     Fof the woodwork as Gerard Cooper's
OL,21,     Fextreme right wing views become
OL,22,     Fmore apparent to the police.
